\fs26 \cf3 \up0 And the rulers said to them, "Let them live, but let them be woodcutters and water carriers for all the congregation, as the rulers had promised them." 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 22
\fs26 \cf3 \up0 Then Joshua called for them, and he spoke to them, saying, "Why have you deceived us, saying, "We are very far from you,' when you dwell near us? 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 23
