\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 3
\fs26 \cf3 \up0 and the eastern Jordan plain from the Sea of Chinneroth as far as the Sea of the Arabah (the Salt Sea), the road to Beth Jeshimoth, and southward below the slopes of Pisgah. 
